What OWASP Juice Shop is (and why itâ€™s different)

OWASP Juice Shop is an intentionally insecure modern web application built using:

JavaScript-heavy frontend (SPA style)

APIs and JSON-based communication

Token/session-based authentication

Realistic e-commerce features (login, cart, orders, feedback, admin panel)

Why Juice Shop matters

